There needs to be an ability to enter subtasks in the High Level Plan.  Most times, the primary task would be something like Initiation but we need to keep track, at a higher level, some Initiation tasks but this does not allow me to do so.  It should be limited to at least 3 levels down.

Many times, a project manager is tracking their project in MS project or other tools but they need to use a PPM tool since it is the source of the truth.  There needs to be a feature to allow the import of mpp files.  You should be able to import it initially to setup the project or import it to update the project's tasks.

If users are used to using MS Project, they can insert a new task by hitting the <Insert> key on their keyboard.  This feature should be supported as well as right clicking on the mouse and clicking Insert task.

There should be a way of having the overall project GYR status calculated.  If the GYR for Scope, Schedule, etc, are yellow or red, the overall project status should be yellow or red.  It should depend on the business rules define.  For example, in the past, if any part of the project was yellow or red, then the Project's status was Yellow or Red.
